se (Fitzgerald, Ga.). Vol. 2, no. 5 (January 15th, 1897) (microfilm surrogate); title from masthead. Volume XVII, number 51 (April 13, 1912) (microfilm surrogate). Fitzgerald leader (Fitzgerald, Ga. : 1910) (DLC)sn 89053299 (OCoLC)19965841 Leader-enterprise (Fitzgerald, Ga.) (DLC)sn 85038489 (OCoLC)12608604"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.046Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-04", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-04"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn89053307/", "image_url": [], "index": 1, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [31.7148055, -83.2515932], "location": ["fitzgerald", "ben hill", "georgia", "ben hill county", "irwin county", "united states"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-83.2515932, 31.7148055], "number": ["2024-05-12t17:32:27.269094", "microfilm master", "2025-07-01t13:40:42.500000", "univ of georgia", "online resource", "sn85038489", "1145", "1", "microfilm service copy", "2995-9675", "sn89053299", "19965838", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn89053307/1902-10-03/ed-1/", "sn89053307", "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn89053307/1912-04-13/ed-1/", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["fitzgerald enterprise (fitzgerald, ga.;fitzgerald, georgia) 1895-1912", "catalog", "chronicling america", "serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["triweekly"], "score": 89.36902, "shelf_id": "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn89053307", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["newspapers", "fitzgerald (ga.)", "irwin county (ga.)", "fitzgerald", "ben hill", "georgia", "ben hill county", "irwin county", "united states", "ben hill county (ga.)"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:28:49.592Z", "title": "Fitzgerald enterprise", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn89053307/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271009/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1895", "dates": ["[1895 TO 1912]"], "description": ["Triweekly, June 13, 1903-Apr. 13, 1912 Print began in December 1895; ceased with volume XVII, number 51 (April 13, 1912). Publisher: Nettie C. Hall, <1897>. Merged with: Fitzgerald leader (Fitzgerald, Ga. : 1910), to form: Leader-enterprise (Fitzgerald, Ga.). Volume VII, Number [?] (October 3, 1902); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Volume XVII, Number 51 (April 13, 1912) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Fitzgerald leader (Fitzgerald, Ga. : 1910) 2995-9705 (DLC) 2024271010 (OCoLC)1288157538 Leader-enterprise (Fitzgerald, Ga.) 2995-9721 (DLC) 2024271011 (OCoLC)1350137676"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:07.154Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271009/", "image_url": [], "index": 2, "language": ["english"], "location": ["irwin", "fitzgerald", "ben hill", "georgia", "ben hill county", "united states"], "number": ["2024271011", "online resource", "2024271009", "2024271010", "1348950650", "2995-9683", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "fitzgerald enterprise (fitzgerald, georgia) 1895-1912 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["triweekly"], "score": 65.189575, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "fitzgerald (ga.)", "irwin", "fitzgerald", "ben hill", "journaux", "georgia", "ben hill county", "united states", "ben hill county (ga.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:38.179Z", "title": "Fitzgerald enterprise", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271009/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271010/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "18??", "dates": ["[1800 TO 1912]"], "description": ["Semiweekly, <Jan. 4, 1911>-Apr. 12, 1912 Ceased with vol. XVII, no. 27 (April 12, 1912). Published also as a daily. Publisher: B.F. Knapp and J.G. Knapp, <January 28, 1910>. Merged with: Fitzgerald enterprise, to form: Leader-enterprise (Fitzgerald, Ga.). Vol. XVII, No. 24 (April 2, 1912); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Vol. XVII, No. 27 (April 12, 1912) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Fitzgerald enterprise 2995-9683 (DLC) 2024271009 (OCoLC)1348950650 Leader-enterprise (Fitzgerald, Ga.) 2995-9721 (DLC) 2024271011 (OCoLC)1350137676"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:01.956Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271010/", "image_url": [], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "location": ["irwin", "fitzgerald", "ben hill", "georgia", "ben hill county", "united states"], "number": ["2024271011", "online resource", "2024271009", "2024271010", "2995-9705", "1288157538", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Issues published Feb. 1-Mar. 11, 1911 with title: Semiweekly Fitzgerald leader"], "partof": ["the fitzgerald leader (fitzgerald, ben hill county georgia) 18??-1912 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["semiweekly"], "score": 65.189575, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["periodical", "newspapers", "fitzgerald (ga.)", "irwin", "fitzgerald", "ben hill", "journaux", "georgia", "ben hill county", "united states", "ben hill county (ga.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:38.179Z", "title": "The Fitzgerald leader", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271010/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271012/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1915", "dates": ["[1915 TO 1915]"], "description": ["Triweekly Began with vol. XX, no. 134 (Nov. 10, 1915); ceased with vol. XX, no. 140 (Nov. 22, 1915). Formed by the union of: Leader-Enterprise (Fitzgerald, Ga.), and: Fitzgerald press. Vol. XX, No. 134 (Nov. 10, 1915); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Vol. XX, No. 140 (Nov. 10, 1915) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Leader enterprise and press 2995-9799 (DLC) 2024271013 (OCoLC)1350104569"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:07.154Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271012/", "image_url": [], "index": 4, "language": ["english"], "location": ["fitzgerald", "ben hill", "georgia", "ben hill county", "united states"], "number": ["2024271011", "online resource", "2995-9748", "2024271012", "2024271013", "1350137653", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["the leader-enterprise and fitzgerald press (fitzgerald, ben hill county, georgia) 1915-1915 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["triweekly"], "score": 65.189575, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "fitzgerald (ga.)", "fitzgerald", "ben hill", "journaux", "georgia", "ben hill county", "united states", "ben hill county (ga.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:38.179Z", "title": "The Leader-enterprise and Fitzgerald press", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271012/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271013/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1915", "dates": ["[1915 TO 1921]"], "description": ["Triweekly Began with vol. XX, no. 141 (Nov. 24, 1915); ceased in March 1921. Vol. XX, No. 141 (Nov. 24, 1915); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Vol. XXVI, No. 29 (March 11, 1921) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Fitzgerald leader enterprise and press 2995-9896 (DLC) 2024271014 (OCoLC)1350136980"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:07.154Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271013/", "image_url": [], "index": 5, "language": ["english"], "location": ["fitzgerald", "ben hill", "georgia", "ben hill county", "united states"], "number": ["online resource", "2024271012", "1350104569", "2995-9799", "2024271015", "2024271013", "2024271014", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the leader enterprise and press (fitzgerald, ben hill county, georgia) 1915-1921 [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["triweekly"], "score": 65.189575, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "fitzgerald (ga.)", "fitzgerald", "ben hill", "journaux", "georgia", "ben hill county", "united states", "ben hill county (ga.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:38.179Z", "title": "The leader enterprise and press", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271013/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271014/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1921", "dates": ["[1921 TO 1964]"], "description": ["Weekly, January 12, 1922-September 10, 1964 Began with vol. XXVI, no. 29 (March 9, 1921); ceased with v. 69, no. 37 (Sept. 10, 1964). \"Official organ of the city of Fitzgerald.\"--vol. XXVI, no. 29 (March 9, 1921), page [4]. Publisher: Fitzgerald Leader Company, Inc., April 4, 1963-September 10, 1964. For some issues in April 1921, stated frequency is \"published daily, tri-weekly.\" Cannot be detemined whether the two frequencies constitute separate editions; they seem more likely to be the same title available in different subscriptions. <March 9-April 1, 1921>, this title may have appeared also as part of Fitzgerald leader (Fitzgerald, Ga. : Daily), constituting the issue for certain days of the week. Merged with: Fitzgerald herald, to form: Fitzgerald herald and the Fitzgerald leader. Vol. XXVI, No. 29 (March 9, 1921); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Vol. XXXVIII, No. 21 (May 26, 1927) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed January 11, 2024). Fitzgerald herald Fitzgerald herald and the Fitzgerald leader"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:38:07.154Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2024271014/", "image_url": [], "index": 6, "language": ["english"], "location": ["fitzgerald", "ben hill", "georgia", "ben hill county", "united states"], "number": ["online resource", "1350136980", "2995-9896", "2024271015", "2024271013", "2024271014", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Occasional issue may bear previous title: Leader enterprise and press"], "partof": ["serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the fitzgerald leader enterprise and press (fitzgerald, georgia) 1921-1964 [online resource]"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 65.189575, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "fitzgerald (ga.)", "fitzgerald", "ben hill", "journaux", "georgia", "ben hill county", "united states", "ben hill county (ga.)"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T21:13:38.179Z", "title": "The Fitzgerald leader enterprise and press", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2024271014/"}], "next_resource": {"label": "Next Issue", "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn89053307/1908-06-27/ed-1/?fo=json&sp=1"}, "options": {"access_group": [""], "access_group_raw": "", "all": null, "api_version": "1", "app_context": null, "application_version": "$Revision$"