mpire Store THE GREATEST THAT HAS EVER HAPPENED PRICES CUT ON EVERY ARTICLE IN BOTH ROOMS FITZGERALDS Industrial and Mercantile Enterprises to be Ex ploited by the AB A Now that the recent financial panic is a thing of the past and conditions are resuming their nor mal state enterprisee and indus tries are once more taking hold of the reins of commerce with a firm hand and where a feeling of tim idity prevailed only a few months ago this has given way to one of secarity and confidence and in the place of stagnation the polluted waters of trade and finance are be coming clear until today we read of industries all over the country that are resuming operations It isa matter of history as to how the A B A R R weath ered the financial storm and in many instances continued the im provement of the croad in pursu ance with their plans Now that prosperity is again sighted on the horizon they are proceeding with their plavs of improvement with renewed vigor and it is with gratification that the people of"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2024-05-22T12:55:27.766Z", "group": ["ndnp/gu", "digital-library-of-georgia-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn89053307/1908-06-25/ed-1/?sp=1", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:gu:batch_gu_cookie_ver02:data:sn89053307:00517177167:1908062501:0934/full/pct:3.125/0/default.jpg#h=298&w=213", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:gu:batch_gu_cookie_ver02:data:sn89053307:00517177167:1908062501:0934/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=596&w=427", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:gu:batch_gu_cookie_ver02:data:sn89053307:00517177167:1908062501:0934/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=1193&w=854", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/gu/batch_gu_cookie_ver02/data/sn89053307/00517177167/1908062501/0934.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 1, "language": ["english"], "location": ["fitzgerald", "ben hill", "g